title: AURORA Duo Chrome Print & Cut
description:
Duo Chrome is the newest of Aurora Graphics print and cut titles. Combining colorful polished surfaces with chrome effects in .pdf format. Its as easy as open, scale, print/cut. With 30 different shapes and 9 unique print effects there are a total of 270 files ready to print and cut! Also included on this DVD are transparent .tiff 
format graphics to be used as a design element in a full body wrap. The .tiff versions also come with an optional drop shadow or a simple beveled transparency of the graphics.

- 270 print/cut ready
  designs in.pdf 
  format 

- .eps files 
  included

- 330 transparent .tiff
